::DevilDuer/Bloodystrike/Perndabot/Reptilica::

DevilDuer looks around at the smoking 'people's base'. He shruggs, looking at 
the other two alliance members there. "Too heated for me," he says, grinning, 
"I think a retreat is in order..."

Bloodystrike and Perndabot look around too. There was really nothing to kill. 
They both nod and the three alliance members set off towards base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica arrives back at the alliance base. He had quietly left the battle 
at the predacon base when the attackers had retreated. He enters the base and 
walks off towards the CR chambers.
